Harry Lewis (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Harry_Lewis_(actor) 0 Harry L. Lewis (April 1, 1920 – June 9, 2013) was a supporting actor in films and was the founder, along with his wife Marilyn, of the "Hamburger Hamlet" restaurant chain.
